---
title: Personal Pizzas with Prosciutto, Artichokes, and Fresh Mozzarella
description: Get a taste of the Mediterranean with these fresh, colorful, and ridiculously easy personal pizzas. We top 'em with homemade marinara and a selection of toppings  guaranteed to make everyone happy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/personal-pizzas-de87b8da.jpg
